summary: This document contains financial data related to settled foreign exchange contracts for the period of July 1, 2013, to July 31, 2013. It details transactions involving New Zealand dollars and U.S. dollars, including amounts, rates, and revalued amounts.
keyFacts: The document lists foreign exchange contracts settled between July 1, 2013, and July 31, 2013.
